 The objectives of this study are: 1.

 .

 To evaluate the diagnostic performance of the assay of the glycosylated ferritin under HLH syndrome and Still's disease in adults.

 2.

 .

 To study the different glycoforms of ferritin from serum of patient with hyperferritinemia.

