 Patient groups studied and control group - Any suspicion of HLH or Still's disease syndrome in adults - Control groups: sepsis, severe sepsis, septic shock, inflammation ( lupus, rheumatoid arthritis), severe hepatic necrosis, hematologic malignancy at diagnosis or relapse 2 .

